<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8" /><title>Event Reminder</title>
<style>
body{font-family:-apple-system,sans-serif;background:#f5f5f5;margin:0;padding:0}
.container{max-width:560px;margin:40px auto;background:#fff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
.header{background:#1a1a2e;padding:32px;text-align:center}
.header h1{color:#fff;margin:0;font-size:22px}.header p{color:#a0aec0;margin:8px 0 0;font-size:14px}
.body{padding:32px}.body p{color:#4a5568;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px}
.event-card{background:#f7fafc;border-left:4px solid #667eea;border-radius:4px;padding:16px 20px;margin:24px 0}
.event-card .title{font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:#2d3748;margin:0 0 8px}
.event-card .meta{font-size:14px;color:#718096;margin:4px 0}
.cta{text-align:center;margin:32px 0 0}
.cta a{background:#667eea;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:inline-block}
.footer{background:#f7fafc;padding:20px 32px;text-align:center}
.footer p{color:#a0aec0;font-size:12px;margin:0}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header"><h1>Event Reminder</h1><p>Your event is coming up in {{reminderLabel}}</p></div>
  <div class="body">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Just a heads up — <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong> is happening in <strong>{{reminderLabel}}</strong>.</p>
    <div class="event-card">
      <p class="title">{{eventTitle}}</p>
      <p class="meta">{{formatDate eventDate}}</p>
      <p class="meta">{{eventVenue}}, {{eventCity}}</p>
    </div>
    <p>Don't forget to bring your ticket QR code. See you there!</p>
    <div class="cta"><a href="{{appUrl}}/events/{{eventId}}">View Event Details</a></div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer"><p>Eventful — Your passport to unforgettable moments.</p></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
